AutoLISP backtrace (most recent call first, 4 frames):
  in SUBR TERPRI: (#<file /tmp/foo>)
  in EVAL: (TERPRI S)
  in USUBR LAMBDA: (#<file /tmp/foo>)
  in EVAL: ((LAMBDA (S) (TERPRI S) (CLOSE S)) (OPEN "/tmp/foo" "a"))
_$ (setq *AUTOLISP-DIALECT* 'lax)
LAX          <----------------------------- FROM HERE ON, IT SHOULD BE LAX ! ---------------
